  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Please download today&#39;s kanji practice here: <a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"../../pdfs/week_04/day_20/Kanji_Practice_Day_20.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Kanji Practice Day 20.pdf</a></p><p>Practising writing kanji every day is a very important exercise to help you learn quickly. If you have any questions you can always ask other students and teachers in the community <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p><p>Refer back to the <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/courses/take/akamonkai-japanese-12-week-beginner-course/texts/18333237-week-4-kanji\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Week 4 - Kanji lesson</a> to watch how to do the correct stroke order for 学, 生, 先.</p></div></div>",
